Class Summary
Carrion Carrion class is a subclass of and represents the food edible by carnivorous.
Cell Overview
A cell represent a generic unit of map.
CellFactory Overview
The class CellFactory is responsible for creating new cells It stores: Its unique instance Collaborators

Food Overview
The class Food stores information about the units of food present in the game
There can be two sorts of Food: Vegetation and Carrion;
Food is the parent class of the Vegetation and Carrion classes.
GraphMap Overview
The GraphMap class instantiate a simple undirected graph which contains all the cells reachable by a dinosaur.
Map Overview
The Map class is a Singleton, it has information about positions of cells and dinosaurs playing.
MapData Overview
The MapData class stores map informations.
